The paper introduces a method for creatively exploring and navigating the latent spaces of deep generative models, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method is used to produce time-based media such as videos, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of a non-linear video editor, which is related to graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper aims to encourage the use of deep generative models as a medium for creative expression, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
